{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/blog/python/convert-wav-or-mp3-to-flac/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Kevin Ponce Blog","author":"Kevin Ponce"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"6c468155-7dbf-5fab-b02d-df6ac72bc8d4","excerpt":"How to convert wav or mp3 to flac using Python. Before you can use the script, you must install dependencies: Install ffmpeg Mac Linux Install pydub Script:","html":"<p>How to convert wav or mp3 to flac using Python.</p>\n<p>Before you can use the script, you must install dependencies:</p>\n<h1>Install ffmpeg</h1>\n<h2>Mac</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">brew install ffmpeg</code></pre></div>\n<h2>Linux</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">sudo apt-get install ffmpeg</code></pre></div>\n<h1>Install pydub</h1>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">pip install pydub</code></pre></div>\n<h1>Script:</h1>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> os<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>path <span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> splitext\n<span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> pydub <span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> AudioSegment\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"token function\">wav_to_flac</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>wav_path<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    flac_path <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"%s.flac\"</span> <span class=\"token operator\">%</span> splitext<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>wav_path<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n    song <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> AudioSegment<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>from_wav<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>wav_path<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n    song<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>export<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>flac_path<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">format</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"flac\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"token function\">mp3_to_flac</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>mp3_path<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    flac_path <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"%s.flac\"</span> <span class=\"token operator\">%</span> splitext<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>mp3_path<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n    song <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> AudioSegment<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>from_mp3<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>mp3_path<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n    song<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>export<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>flac_path<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">format</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"flac\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\nmp3_to_flac<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"test_split3.mp3\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>","frontmatter":{"title":"Python convert wav or mp3 to flac","date":"November 26, 2020","description":"How to convert wav or mp3 to flac using Python.","author":null}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/python/convert-wav-or-mp3-to-flac/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/python/http/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Python http","tags":["python"]}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/film/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Film School Notes","tags":["postgres"]}}}}}